title: NOAA NDFD, Wind speed forecast for Sept 02, 2008 along the gulf coast, USA, Aug 29, 2008
name: NOAA NDFD, Wind speed forecast for Sept 02, 2008 along the gulf coast, USA, Aug 29, 2008
description: The point shapefile shows data for the windspeed forecast for 2nd Sept, 2008 along parts of Gulf coast, near the site where hurricane Gustav may make a land-fall. The 7 day forecast is based on NOAA's NDFD as of 29th Aug, 2008.
